data.description: Welcome to Living on Lake Street. At this well maintained 5 bedroom, 2 bath townhouse you are able to discover the elegance and comfort of your dream home. Enjoy the convenience of an attached 2 car garage that boasts plenty of space for your vehicles and storage needs. From the spacious bedrooms to the freshly stained deck overlooking one of the many serene community ponds you have a great deal of perfect spots to unwind and soak in the beauty of your surroundings. The spacious bedrooms and modern amenities throughout this townhouse also offers the ideal combination of style and functionality. Experience the allure of this beautiful townhouse that awaits for you to call it home sweet home. Don't delay, the seller is so motivated, seller giving $5,000 toward closing cost, contact us now to book your tour!
